{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1695-03_188","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"[Epistre à Mr le Duc de Vendosme]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mars 1695 [tome 3], p. 188-196.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Je vous envoye une Epistre en Vers, dont le tour est aisé &amp; naturel, &amp; fait voir que l’Auteur sçait le monde. Il est moins difficile de s’élever que d’attraper ce stile d’honneste homme, que tous les gens de bon goust estiment, &amp; qu’ils trouvent dans peu d’Ouvrages.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#":[{"hi":{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"À M. le Duc","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[0]/hi/#"}}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"DE VENDOSME,","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[2]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"Sur sa nomination au Generalat des Galeres.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[4]/#"}}]}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vendosme, malgré moy, je cède aux deux transports","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du Dieu des Vers qui m’anime,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je sens malgré mes efforts","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que d’une involontaire rime","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce Dieu va former les accords.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" C’estoit assez que la Prose","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Modeste, &amp; sans ornement","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De Toy nous dist quelque chose","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour te loüer dignement.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car, mon Prince, c’est d’un songe","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tirer des réalitez,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’emprunter les vanitez","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[11]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du langage du mensonge,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour dire tes veritez.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[13]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Laissons à la Renommée","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Publier tes actions,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui paroistroient fictions,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si tu n’avois dans l’Armée,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A nostre perte animée,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour témoins, vingt Nations.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est cette seule Déesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui par tout suivit tes pas,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui doit chanter ta sagesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ton sang froid dans les combats.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle seule peut bien dire","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jusques où va ton ardeur,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et ce que doit cet Empire","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A ton bras, à ta valeur.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[13]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" C’est elle qui dans les airs,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour Toy, deployant ses ailes ?","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Porte tes grandeurs nouvelles","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aux deux bouts de l’Univers,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui planant sur la Marsaille","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Te vit, à cette Bataille,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Couvrir de morts les sillons,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où dans un étroit passage","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’opposoient à ton courage","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les plus épais Bataillons.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Icy c’est plûtost aux hommes,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est à tous tant que nous sommes","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui ressentons ta bonté,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’aller publiant sans cesse","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quel air haut, quelle noblesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Brille en ta simplicité ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De quel prix inestimable","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour nous est un Prince aimable","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui sçait accorder si bien,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Loin de toute fierté vaine,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aux talens d’un Capitaine,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les vertus d’un Citoyen.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[11]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Quoy donc, le Dieu qui m’enflame,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qui, bien ou mal, m’apprit","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’art de loüer ta grande ame,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne dit rien de ton esprit ?","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour te plaire davantage,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Apollon l’a fait exprés.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il sçait combien tu te plais,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans un simple badinage,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelquefois à l’oublier","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et croiroit commettre un crime,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout grand qu’il est, tout sublime,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’oser l’aller publier.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[11]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais où suis-je ? quelle yvresse","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Hors de moy m’a transporté ?","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’entens des cris d’allegresse.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quel bruit d’un autre costé","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vient de frapper mon oreille ?","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je vois du Port de Marseille,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout ce pompeux appareil,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et nos Galeres parées","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Faire briller au Soleil,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Leurs magnifiques livrées.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’entens ces Reines des Mers","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des cris de mille coupables,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et des voix des miserables,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Former de charmans concerts.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[13]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Je le vois, sur sa Galere","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce General est monté.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Déja son humanité","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans le sein de la misere,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A fait naistre la gayeté,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et déja son air affable,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A dans ce sejour affreux","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Consolé ces malheureux,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Seurs que son cœur pitoyable,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De leurs maux se touchera,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que sensible à leurs peines,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne pouvant briser leurs chaisnes,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sa main les relaschera.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[12]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Fuyez, Galeres d’Espagne,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Desormais loin de ces bords.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Allez cacher dans vos Ports","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La peur qui vous accompagne ;","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vendosme s’en va sur vous","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Bientost lancer ce tonnerre","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont tans de fois sur la terre","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il a fait sentir les coups,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et je vois déja Neptune,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui pour plaire à Jupiter","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’empresse de luy prester","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Son Trident &amp; sa Fortune.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[11]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ainsi par la bienveillance,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De ce grand Roy des François,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui déja dessous tes loix","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avoit remis sa Provence,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu vois croistre ta puissance,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et l’un &amp; l’autre élément.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Charmé de son esclavage,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Se disputer l’avantage","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’obéir aveuglément.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[8]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[18]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" D’une telle confiance,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mon Prince, connoy le prix,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est l’effet de la prudence,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De la bonté de Louis.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ton Roy sçait pour sa Personne","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quel est ton attachement,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’en luy tu crois la Couronne","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Son plus leger ornement,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour l’Etat quel est ton zele,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et d’un Sujet si fidele.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il connoist le dévouëment ;","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et c’est cette connoissance","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui seule fait ton bonheur,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et la seule récompense","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui pouvoit flatter ton cœur.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[14]/#"}}]}}]}}}